.
I don't know if I ever expressed it, but Im always so conflicted when I want to post smth where a part is on Patreon... I want to make so much I can make everyone happy but then again even more additional stuff for my Patreons who pay money for it... I tried making 2 comics at a time at first posting 1here and 2 there, without you even noticing you were getting less, but I'm just too slow to be able to do that... I wish I wouldn't have to sleep anymore it would make so much much easier...

Do you prefer the old or the new hero costume? Tbh I wasn't quite sure with this one 👉👈 Also I'm sorry for saying I had everyone from class 1a when I was still missing Mr sparkle boy here 😫💖
.
Do you have a tattoo? Well, these 2 now have some^^ 
.
Headcanon: Aoyama and Denki were the only ones excepting Mineta throughout his 2nd and 3rd year of highschool. Despite him really trying and looking his best. In his 3rd year he started to distance himself from Denki a bit though. He realized Denki would always be seen as that charming a little per<y character he introduced himself as, while mineta never had his charm.
.
Later he wanted to keep things low first and learn how other pro heroes around him behaved to be excepted from the public. So he became a side kick first (Not Aoyamas btw tough. But working for the same agency)
.
Aoyama is so much fun to draw 😫❤️ I hope I get to draw him more in the future 💖
.
I'm still thinking about who's agency to put them in tough hmmmmmmmm 🤔
